translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「剣の腕が中々立つのに加えて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Not only is her sword skill quite good,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 目つきが悪く愛想もない女だぞ、見ての通り」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: She's got a harsh look and no charm, as you can see."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お近づきになりたいと思う程度にはな、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: get a lot closer to her,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「というわけで、お互いをもっとよく知るために、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "So then, to get to know each other better,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここは一つベッドで作戦会議でも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: let's have a strategy meeting on the bed!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しようではないか！　がははははははは！」
「こう見えても主婦だぞ、私は」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Believe it or not, I'm a housewife."
"By the way, I also have children.
A son who's three years old."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私のような戦しか能のない女を、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "There was a strange man who fell in love with a woman like me,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 好きになる奇っ怪な男がいたのだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: who only knows how to fight."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、旦那がいようと俺は気にしない。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, even if you have a husband, I don't care.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺と浮気するぞ、これは命令だ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm ordering you to cheat on him with me."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちんぼこ引き千切って口に詰め込むぞ貴様」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I'll tear off your dick and shove it into your mouth, you bastard."
"Sorry, that was my true nature showing."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 中庭では紀伊が刀を振るっていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the courtyard, Kii was swinging her sword.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ほー、中々やるもんじゃないか。

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're diligent with your training, I'm impressed."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「刀を振るうなどもう五年ぶりなのでな、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's been five years since I last swung a sword,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 出来るだけ勘を取り戻したいんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so I want to regain my sense as much as possible."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちっとも刀振るってなかったのか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You haven't swung your sword at all?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ、今の旦那と籍を入れてからは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Yeah, ever since I married my current husband,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 刀は捨てて専業主婦として生きてきた」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I threw away my sword and lived as a full-time housewife."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 武将に登用しようって奴もいたろう。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'm sure there were people who wanted to recruit you as a commander.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どんな生活をしてきたんだ、君は？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What kind of life have you lived?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 我が家は巫女機関とゆかりのある家でな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: My family is connected to the Miko organization.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 刀や薙刀における戦闘指南役だったらしい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: which served as combat instructors for sword and naginata use."
